Class DynFormUserAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.yawlfoundation.yawl.resourcing.jsf.dynform.DynFormUserAttributes

  • public class DynFormUserAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages the set of user-defined (at design-time) extended attributes of a workitem, some of which will affect the way the dynamic form is displayed. Author: Michael Adams Date: 24/02/2009
